<span id="freeTextContainer8101117389441391593">**I received this book for free through Goodreads First Reads.**<br/><br/>Not a lot to say about this book except that I expected one thing and got another.<br/><br/>What I expected: Stories of widowhood.<br/><br/>What I got: A what to do/not to do guide for handling the recently widowed.<br/><br/>What I liked: It made me think. Made me realize that the best thing I can do for someone is to just be there and listen.<br/> <br/>What I didn’t like: I was not a fan of the layout. Instead of hearing multiple voices, I felt like I was only hearing on</span>
  <span id="freeText8101117389441391593" style="display:none">**I received this book for free through Goodreads First Reads.**<br /><br />Not a lot to say about this book except that I expected one thing and got another.<br /><br />What I expected: Stories of widowhood.<br /><br />What I got: A what to do/not to do guide for handling the recently widowed.<br /><br />What I liked: It made me think. Made me realize that the best thing I can do for someone is to just be there and listen.<br /> <br />What I didn’t like: I was not a fan of the layout. Instead of hearing multiple voices, I felt like I was only hearing one.<br /></span>
