  <span id="freeText1586071828133339127" style="display:none">“The Widow or Widower Next Door” is a one of a kind collection of stories, remembrances, and advice written by several different widows and widowers. MaryLee Robinson’s aim with this project is to get people thinking about how they can better support, help and talk with the people in our lives experiencing loss. The first hand stories are touching, thoughtful and provide great insight to those that want to help, but don’t quite know how to. If you have friends or family going through a loss, or have been through one yourself, this book is a must read!</span>
