<span id="freeTextContainer9557786617985370412">Mary Lee is a native Baltimorian, by way of 5 recent years in Charleston, WV with her husband Pat. They moved to the Low County of South Carolina together and enjoyed their time together there immensely, until Pat died suddenly.<br/><br/>She attended Virginia Tech, is a former Army Reservist, enjoyed a career in sales, property and construction management. <br/><br/>Mary Lee has now turned her attention to<br/>reaching ou</span>
  <span id="freeText9557786617985370412" style="display:none">Mary Lee is a native Baltimorian, by way of 5 recent years in Charleston, WV with her husband Pat. They moved to the Low County of South Carolina together and enjoyed their time together there immensely, until Pat died suddenly.<br /><br />She attended Virginia Tech, is a former Army Reservist, enjoyed a career in sales, property and construction management. <br /><br />Mary Lee has now turned her attention to<br />reaching out to other widows and widowers with her books (there's a second in the planning), and establishing social clubs for widows and widowers, one by one, and dreams of a network of clubs across the country. </span>
